metadata.name: Happy Planet Club #1
metadata.description: Welcome to your new home. A place where everything is possible and sadness is unknown. Find your perfect purpose, mix up with your fellow brothers and be happy. Happy Planet Club is a free-mint NFT collection on the ETH blockchain consisting of 3,000 tokens. Our characters are divided into 5 different races. Find a great variety of traits and unique combinations. No promises, no roadmap, just art.
